# Orchestration

Subagent definitions live in `.cursor/agents/`.

| Work type | Delegate to |
|-----------|-------------|
| Train/eval, rewards, checkpoints, logs, hyperparameters, approach comparison | **ai-rl-sme** |
| Refactors, packaging, typing, tests, CLI, `common/` API, dependencies | **dev** |
| Both | **dev** implements; **ai-rl-sme** runs experiments and updates the code repo `memory-bank/` |

Pass each subagent: target **repo id** from `registry/projects.yaml`, environment name (if any), and paths to tier-1 context files.

After RL work, ensure the code repo `memory-bank/` is updated before closing the task.
